rem *** Custom Animated Flags (if added via con files for game mode instead of in staticobjects.con file) ***
rem *** must have their animation states loaded from a con file loaded in via one of the game mode con ***
rem *** files. Conquest.con file for example. ***


AnimationStateMachine.createState Belfry_Flag_Idle
AnimationStateMachine.addAnimation Animations/Belfry_Flag_Idle.baf 1 1
AnimationStateMachine.setMorphFactor 1
AnimationStateMachine.set3pAnimationSpeed Belfry_Flag_Idle 0.1



